'''DNA聚合酶δ'''（{{lang|en|DNA polymerase delta}}）為[[真核生物|真核生物]]體內的一種[[酶|酶]]複合體，可進行[[DNA复制|DNA复制]]及[[DNA修復|修復]]。DNA聚合酶δ由四個次單元組成：{{tsl|en|POLD1|POLD1}}、{{tsl|en|POLD2|POLD2}}、{{tsl|en|POLD3|POLD3}}，以及{{tsl|en|POLD4|POLD4}}<ref name="pmid16934752">{{cite journal |vauthors=Liu G, Warbrick E | title = The p66 and p12 subunits of DNA polymerase delta are modified by ubiquitin and ubiquitin-like proteins | journal = Biochem. Biophys. Res. Commun. | volume = 349 | issue = 1 | pages = 360–6 |date=October 2006 | pmid = 16934752 | doi = 10.1016/j.bbrc.2006.08.049 | url = | issn = }}</ref>。本酵素可進行延遲股及領先股的複製<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Johnson RE, Klassen R, Prakash L, Prakash S |title=A Major Role of DNA Polymerase δ in Replication of Both the Leading and Lagging DNA Strands  |journal=Mol. Cell. |volume=59 |issue=2 |pages=163–175 |date=July 16, 2015 |pmid= 26145172 |doi=10.1016/j.molcel.2015.05.038 |pmc=4517859}}</ref><ref>http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov.elibrary.mdanderson.org/pubmed/?term=DNA+Polymerases+Divide+the+Labor+of+Genome+Replication{{Dead link|date=2019年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。若{{tsl|en|PCNA|PCNA}}存在，該酵素的持續效能會增強。

